data.title: Luke Bryan’s Wife Joins Him Onstage To Sing ‘Sweet Caroline’
data.meta_description: Luke Bryan and his wife are once again showing off how cute they are.  During a cover song-filled concert in Cancun, Mexico, on Jan. 22, she joined her hubby on stage to sing "Sweet Caroline."
data.text:
This is too cute.

Luke Bryan and his wife are once again showing off how cute they are. According to tasteofcountry.com During a cover song-filled concert in Cancun, Mexico, on Jan. 22, she joined her hubby on stage to sing “Sweet Caroline.”

The adorable moment was videotaped and has been shared online. Luke has sung “Sweet Caroline” many times while performing, and it is a fan favorite. Luke is certainly one of the good guys! We love you both Luke and Caroline! Keep singing.
